These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, soy-milk, sprite
City: nizza, boston, paris, berlin
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, apricot, coral, aquamarine
4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, canasta, chess
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, jazz, rock
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, havana, davidoff, game
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite, sunflower, zinnia
 1. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing snooker is the person traveling to boston##1
 3. the person traveling to berlin is the havana-smoker##1
 4. the davidoff-smoker is the person traveling to boston##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who likes coral##2
 6. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is the montecristo-smoker##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing canasta is the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
12. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
13. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the fan of rock##1
14. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
16. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
17. the game-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
18. the game-smoker is the person who growszinnia##1
19. the fan of folk is the person traveling to nizza##1
20. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
21. the person playing snooker is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | sprite        | soy-milk   | 7up         | iced-tea  |
| City          | paris         | boston   | nizza   | berlin |
| Color         | coral | apricot    | aquamarine | green   |
| Game   | monopoly        | snooker  | chess      | canasta   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz          | rock       | folk        | ambient   |
| Cigar           | game        | davidoff      | montecristo    | havana    |
| Flower         | zinnia | sunflower | amaryllis      | aconite   |

