House: wooden, tower, futuristic, townhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, architect, dancer, police-officer
City: nizza, new-york, marseilles, berlin
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, train, trike
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 2. the tower house is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 3. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 5. the prince-smoker is the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 7. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
10. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the bus is the futuristic house##1
12. the tower house is on the right of the police-officer##1
13. the software-developer is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
14. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
15. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
16. the person playing whist is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
17. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
18. the architect is the person driving the trike##1
19. the fan of trance is on the far left or far right##3
20. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
21. the dunhill-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |    4     |
