The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, scientific, action
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, november, february, april
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indonesian, malaysian, nigerian
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, firefighter, mechanic, photographer
4 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, backgammon, billiard
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, aquamarine, emerald, lavender
 1. the person watching scientific movies is between the canadian and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 2. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 3. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person drinking sportsade##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 5. the nigerian is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 6. the mechanic is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is in an odd position##4
10. the scientist is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
11. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
12. the person watching sports movies is the person who likes blue##1
13. the person who likes emerald is in an even position##4
14. the scientist is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
15. the nigerian is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
16. the nigerian is on the left of the indonesian##1
17. the mechanic is the person playing domino##1
18. the malaysian is on the right of the firefighter##1
19. the photographer is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
