City: liverpool, berlin, prague, boston
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
 2. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 7. the person eating banana is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 9. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
10. the person eating potato is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the victorian house is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
14. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
15. the person drinking water is between the person who growstulip and the person traveling to prague##2
16. the farmhouse house is between the person playing chess and the owner of the mouse##2
17. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
18. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |     4      |
